@(1-4=c2513.A.1) Lady of the princely powers, emerging brilliantly like the daylight, chosen forever for her virtuous beauty! @wDN{Nanaya}, ornament of @wTN{E-ana}, worthy of the Lady! Wise one, correctly chosen as lady of all the lands by the Mistress: @wDN{Nanaya}, you instruct the Land, bestowing wisdom in @wTN{E-ana}.

