@(5=c2513.A.5) @fsux{Barsud}.

#lg B	cagbatuku


@(6-11=c2513.B.6) As fine as @wDN{An}, woman with a holy (?) head, made perfect by the …… lady! @wDN{Nanaya}, properly educated by holy @wDN{Inana}, woman who is as bright as the stars, wise lady who is available for everything, righteous sympathetic woman, lady who is always available on request, counselled by holy @wDN{Inana}, beloved by the Mistress! @wDN{Nanaya}, great judge, deity who occupies the high throne of @wSN{Unug}!

